<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        width: 1200px;
        height: 630px;
        font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #1a1a1a;
        color: white;
        position: relative;
      }
      
      .badge {
        position: absolute;
        top: 60px;
        left: 60px;
        background: #ff5722;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 30px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      
      .content {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 60px;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 84px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff5722, #ffc107);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
      }
      
      p {
        font-size: 28px;
        opacity: 0.8;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      
      .date {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 60px;
        right: 60px;
        font-size: 20px;
        opacity: 0.6;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="badge">NEW FEATURE</div>
    <div class="content">
      <h1>Big Announcement!</h1>
      <p>We're excited to share something amazing with you. Stay tuned for more details.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="date">Coming Soon</div>
  </body>
</html>